# ── RindiX environment ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to ".env" and paste your Google Gemini API key below.
# Get a key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#
# NOTE: Because this is a client-side prototype, the key is bundled into
# the front-end. That is fine for a hackathon demo. For production, proxy
# the Gemini call through a tiny serverless function so the key stays secret.

# Your Gemini API key (required for live photo recognition).
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Vision model. The original spec said gemini-1.5-flash, but Google has RETIRED
# the 1.5 models (the API now returns 404), so the default is current 2.5 Flash.
# Other working options: gemini-flash-latest, gemini-2.5-flash-lite.
VITE_GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
